unctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>In the above code, we have used <code class=\"language-text\">btn-lg</code> <code class=\"language-text\">btn-sm</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">btn-xs</code> class to center the button.</p>\n<p>Check the output of the above code example.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d276f839dac697593b14cc8ee586798d/eea4a/button.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 32.278481012658226%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Bootstrap, button\"\n        title=\"Bootstrap, button\"\n        src=\"/static/d276f839dac697593b14cc8ee586798d/828fb/button.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d276f839dac697593b14cc8ee586798d/ff44c/button.jpg 158w,\n/static/d276f839dac697593b14cc8ee586798d/a6688/button.jpg 315w,\n/static/d276f839dac697593b14cc8ee586798d/828fb/button.jpg 630w,\n/static/d276f839dac697593b14cc8ee586798d/0ede0/button.jpg 945w,\n/static/d276f839dac697593b14cc8ee586798d/3ac88/button.jpg 1260w,\n/static/d276f839dac697593b14cc8ee586798d/eea4a/button.jpg 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>All the best üëç</p>","